Date: 1995-03-27

Title: Exact Results in Softly Broken Supersymmetric Models

Authors: Nick Evans, Stephen D.H. Hsu and Myckola Schwetz

Comments: 13 pages, latex; expanded references and discussion of D terms

Journal-ref: Phys. Lett. B355 (1995) 475

We show how recent exact results in supersymmetric theories can be extendedto models which include {\it explicit} soft supersymmetry breaking terms. Wethus derive new exact results for non-supersymmetric models.